text:
The Ippt machine is not reliable and the FI isn't doing anything.
1 FI to 2 machines but idk what they are doing.
Waste of effort and time.
Travelling is inconvenient too, most transport ends at khatib or yishun then you'll have to walk 30 mins to the place.
Attended on 25th June for IPPT. The conduct was excellent and professional. The facilities were also well maintained with easy-to-use lockers and a spacious changing room.
No safe check-in procedure despite in such crucial times? Asked the guard and he said no trace together check in required...
The variety of commerical trainers keep our manhood high and motivate all to do well for their ippt
